        key - key for item to upload

        accessLevel - Storage access level
        targetIdentityId - If set, this should override the current user's identity ID. If null, the operation will fetch the current identity ID.
        contentType - The standard MIME type describing the format of the object to store
        serverSideEncryption - server side encryption type for the current storage bucket
        metadata - Metadata for the object to store
